description: Try our easy to follow Pumpkin Frittatas + Snacks recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Frittata,Pescatarian,Low salt,Egg,Pumpkin,Low sugar,Halal,High protein,High fibre,Mandarin,Vegetarian,Peanut free
name: Pumpkin Frittatas + Snacks Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 12g brown rice crackers no added salt (approx. 9 crackers)

recipeInstructions.text: Lightly grease and line the base of 4 holes of a 12-cup muffin pan with a round of baking paper.
Whisk 3 free range eggs and 2 tbs full cream milk together in a medium bowl. Stir in 3/4 cup (90g) grated Kent pumpkin and 30g grated Cheese. Spoon mixture into prepared muffin holes.
Bake for 20-25 minutes or until filling is set, puffed and golden. Set aside to cool completely.

Pack 2 frittatas next to frozen drink or cool brick in lunch box to keep cool. Snack 1: Serve 9 rice crackers with 1tbs hummus. Snack 2: Place yoghurt in a small airtight plastic container, top with sunflower seeds and drizzle with the honey. note: pumpkin frittata recipe serves 2
